readme

requirements to run the system:

1. docker : run the following command on the terminal after installing docker and the postgres image

docker run --name postgres-container -e POSTGRES_USER=postgres -e POSTGRES_PASSWORD=mysecretpassword -e POSTGRES_DB=DB -d -p 127.0.0.1:5432:5432 postgres

this initialises the DB with the following parameters
DB name : DB
user : postgres
password : mysecretpassword
host: localhost
port : 5432



Indexes
1. ALTER TABLE loginData ADD CONSTRAINT unique_userName_lower UNIQUE (LOWER(userName));